{"tid":473412,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【北京奪19命大火】記者採訪被要求刪相 當局全方位封鎖消息","createTime":"2017-11-19T08:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T16:46:15.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"6ab7d4d13cf08901f3f0f6f3ddea3ca8d15178f0","tid":473412,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171119/large/1511076709_237a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171119%2Flarge%2F1511076709_237a.jpg&h=3aa34a47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n北京大興一出租公寓，昨日傍晚發生大火，造成最少19人死亡，8人受傷，涉事者已被當局拘查。多維新聞報道，事發後，除了網上消息被封鎖，災場同樣被執法部門重重封鎖，當區居民有家歸不得。有在場採訪的記者拍照後，被人要求刪除照片，有當地媒體記者也未能得到一些信息。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171119/57477686\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171119%2F57477686&d=z8Odz5WTuLjKS5UI7fG9KfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=1513ca58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171119%2F57477686&h=224d068c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171119/57477686</a>"},{"pid":"bca43552d5f2ec1af8c9c329d32505aa08390e82","tid":473412,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:11:15.000Z","msg":"縱火案後封鎖消息 網民：政府要給個交代！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n北京巿大興區昨日傍晚發生一宗出租公寓昨晚發生大火警，造成最少19人死亡、8人受傷。當局指已將疑犯扣查。內地的社交媒體全面封殺這場火警的消息．「北京」、「西紅門」等字眼全被封鎖，搜尋亦只會出現「根據相關法律法規和政策，搜尋結果未予顯示」，「不少當地網民質疑19條人命！難道不應該引起全國人民的關注嗎？​」不斷嘗試發文公開事件，但卻遭「秒和諧了」。<br />\n<br />\n網民對當局封鎖消息，極度憤怒：「現在信息這麼發達，這年代還愚弄百姓？」「北京西紅門，不要甚麼都封鎖行嗎？」「出這麼大的事，微博上就沒有一絲絲新聞&hellip;&hellip;」「政府要給個交代！」<br />\n<br />\n由於事件涉及縱火，當局疑似擔心事件影響社會穩定，即時全力封鎖消息，各大網頁僅使用新華社官方資料及相片，新華社的相片疑似「刻意」沒有任何火光或災情，僅有火勢已撲滅完的現場相。新浪微博相關帖子亦被刪走。<br />\n<br />\n網民意見：<br />\n<br />\n紫禁城競技：這次大會這麼嚴重，官方只字不提，難道有不願泄漏的隱情？<br />\n<br />\n1旗幟1：封鎖消息了<br />\n<br />\n愛GuoAn1信仰：很意外，帖子都刪了 為什麼剛BTV的北京您早還報道<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171119/57476563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171119%2F57476563&d=z8Odz5WTuLjKS5UI7fG9KfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=72ac3f97\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171119%2F57476563&h=8a4031c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20171119/57476563</a>"},{"pid":"a472d8578a2b2ea9091670a5d455f5c935d82546","tid":473412,"uid":22858,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-ZgXLysvzBv8/UJpcUjLy6uI/AAAAAAAAAcs/_KN4eCwYtos/s1600/hkflagIl759.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F1.bp.blogspot.com%2F-ZgXLysvzBv8%2FUJpcUjLy6uI%2FAAAAAAAAAcs%2F_KN4eCwYtos%2Fs1600%2FhkflagIl759.gif&h=88ac342b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>五毛say something，係咪好驚下個到你就無糧出</strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：<del><span style=\"color: red;\">三色貓</span></del>、<